<h1>Eldest director</h1>

<% matching_records = Director.where.not({ :dob => nil }).order({ :dob => :asc }) %>

<% @the_eldest_director = matching_records.at(0) %>

<p>The eldest director in our dataset right now is <a href="/directors/<%= @the_eldest_director.id %>"><%= @the_eldest_director.name %></a>, born on <%= @the_eldest_director.dob.strftime("%B %e, %Y") %>.</p>
(<a href="http://strftime.net/">http://strftime.net/</a> is handy for putting together the formatting strings for the <code>.strftime</code> method.)</p>
